id: pm-pee5
title: "Extend the existing pm-brief package with flow metrics: cycle/lead time, throughput, and aging-WIP computed from item history streams"
description: "Best-practice PM flow metrics (cycle time, lead time, throughput, aging WIP, cumulative flow) computed from the status-transition timestamps already in per-item history streams. EXTENDS the existing unbraind/pm-brief package (confirmed live via gh repo list; pm-gantt-chart/pm-ops/pm-context split the rest of the reporting space) — no new package, no new core command; metric computation lands on SDK history read primitives so pm-web/pm-ops can reuse it."
type: Feature
status: open
priority: 3
tags[4]: agent-ux,"area:sdk",packages,reporting
